  <Annotation SID="8061">
    <P Name="Name">Note 2:
It is also important to remark that it is here
supposed that the sensors are located on the x axis,
that all coordinates regard the y axis are null.
(As it actually is the case for most cars in CarMaker,
especially the DemoCar)</P>
    <P Name="Position">[37, 342, 269, 422]</P>
    <P Name="InternalMargins">[0, 0, 0, 0]</P>
    <P Name="ZOrder">-4</P>
  </Annotation>
  <Annotation SID="8062">
    <P Name="Name">Note 1 :
In our case, the two sensors
are located in the same position
which also is the position of the ceter of mass.
(Refer to the Reference Manual)</P>
    <P Name="Position">[54, 271, 259, 338]</P>
    <P Name="InternalMargins">[0, 0, 0, 0]</P>
    <P Name="ZOrder">-5</P>
